hopobject.body: I'll text you later www.herbal ignite Many of us had merely a fleeting affair with high tops -let's face it if you're not blessed with legs up to your armpits they aren't the most pin lengthening footwear style out there. And while many of you may have returned back to the comfort of your Converse (that's us included) Miranda Kerr proved she's still firmly in the Isabel Marant high top camp, by teaming her suede wedge trainers with wet look leggings and a silk scarf by Hermes.
